<li id="cite_note-doctorate-2">^ <a href="#cite_ref-doctorate_2-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-doctorate_2-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> He conferred a <a href="/wiki/Juris_Doctor" title="Juris Doctor">doctorate of law</a> on himself from <a href="/wiki/Makerere_University" title="Makerere University">Makerere University</a>. <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news">"<a href="http://www.news24.com/News24/Africa/News/0,,2-11-1447_1390595,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.news24.com/News24/Africa/News/0,,2-11-1447_1390595,00.html" rel="nofollow">Idi Amin: a byword for brutality</a>". <i><a href="/wiki/News24" title="News24">News24</a></i>. 2003-07-21<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.news24.com/News24/Africa/News/0,,2-11-1447_1390595,00.html" class="external free" title="http://www.news24.com/News24/Africa/News/0,,2-11-1447_1390595,00.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.news24.com/News24/Africa/News/0,,2-11-1447_1390595,00.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-12-02</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Idi+Amin%3A+a+byword+for+brutality&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BNews24%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=2003-07-21&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news24.com%2FNews24%2FAfrica%2FNews%2F0%2C%2C2-11-1447_1390595%2C00.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Idi_Amin"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
